text:
In a romantic atmosphere .. Mai Omar sparkling white with her husband
06 Nov 2019, 06:33 by Aya Altaiji
Aya al-Tiji Director Mohammad Sami published a photo that he shared with his wife Mai Omar, through his official account on Instagram, has appeared in a romantic and charming atmosphere. She wore a short pocket in white, with a white top as well, while choosing a long boot with the same color as her clothes. She chose to highlight the beauty of her eyes with an eye liner with Kashmiri as a lipstick. Let Mai Omar look good by wearing some simple and elegant accessories, and she chose a silver necklace around her neck.
